    <section id="privacy">
        <h2>Privacy Policy</h2>
        <div class="text-block">
            <p><strong>Your Data is Yours.</strong></p>
            <p>At TraceLog, we prioritize your privacy. Your location data is used solely for the purpose of mapping your activities. We do not sell your personal data to third parties.</p>
            <p>You have full control over the visibility of your logs. Choose to keep them private for your own journal, or make them public to share with the community.</p>
            <p>Your data is saved on the cloud securely using Google Firebase</p>
            <p>You can delete your account and all associated data at any time from the settings menu.</p>
            <p>This project is entirely open source. The source code and project files can be found on <a href="https://github.com/IsaacPlays20/TraceLog">Github</a></p>
